node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jason Capital on September 07, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, people standing and indoor.

node.text:
WTF? Let’s unpack this photo: I was 27, teaching a workshop on communication. I wore a suit (because Dan Pena told me I should trade in my casual wear for suits). The student on the ground is doing push-ups. He’s doing push-ups because at my events, if your phone goes off, you do push-ups. So yes, studies have shown people who attend my events have larger pec muscles than any other event in the world. 😂 Today I’m 32 and I don’t wear suits. But if your phone goes off at one of my events, you will hit the floor and give me 20. 

P.S. Do you like Instagram? My team and I are looking for a few more ppl who want to earn a full-time income from home just typing messages on social media. If you’re interested, message me the word “Side hustle”. Thanks!

node.text:
THROWBACK to me and @natalybiskay working at our Villa in Thailand. Do you remember freely traveling to other countries? I do. 😢 Seriously this villa was awesome and the views are insane but the cook there made the best chicken pad thai I’d ever had. Holy shit 😂 

P.S. Have you ever thought about Passive Income? My team and I are looking for a few more ppl who want to earn a full-time passive income from home using AirBNB without owning property. If you’re interested, message me the word “Air bnb”. Thanks
